  "texts": [
    "InterventionA third opportunity for LLMs in the mental health domain is to implement mental health interventions (see Figure 3).",
    "To date, such efforts have largely focused on chatbots.",
    "Prominent chatbots, some of which are LLM-based, include Woebot [27], Wysa [28], Tess [29], Replika [30], Ellie [31], and Sibly [32].",
    "Many of these chatbots were trained in empirically supported treatments such as cognitive behavioral therapy, dialectical behavior therapy, and motivational interviewing.",
    "There is initial evidence that such chatbots may be effective in reducing depressive and anxiety symptoms, as well as stress [33][34][35][36]."
  ],
